data.description: A beautiful home ready for you to move in! Recently renovated corner lot near the quiet Redlands offers a modern kitchen with granite counters, and sliding shelves in the pantry. The newly installed impact windows allow all the Florida sunshine to stream in without the heat and humidity. The temperature control, lighting, and oven range are smart design with app control. The 4 bedrooms are split floor plan. The master bedroom has double-door entry, a walk-in closet, a master bath with soaking tub and separate shower. The backyard is spacious enough to store a boat/trailer/RV and still have room for a pool/playground/shed or any outdoor pleasure. No HOA. Quiet neighborhood with easy access to Homestead ARB, the Everglades, Florida Keys, outlet shopping, diverse dining, and farmer markets.
